title: Paris Hilton flashes underboob on Christian Cowan catwalk | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share The blonde celebutante also donned a towering tiara with a silver-sequinned turtleneck bridal gown for the show's big finish. As usual, Hilton sported her signature waist-length blonde hair extensions as well as false lashes and bright pink eyeshadow. Paris - who boasts 28.6M followers - wrote on Instagram: 'Backstage getting ready to rock the @ChristianCowan runway show. #NYFW' Thigh's the limit: The blonde celebutante also donned a towering tiara with a silver-sequinned turtleneck bridal gown for the show's big finish Weee! As usual, Hilton sported her signature waist-length blonde hair extensions as well as false lashes and bright pink eyeshadow 'Ready to slay the runway!' Curiously, the Donald Trump supporter kept her black hat and large sunglasses on at all times backstage Curiously, the Donald Trump supporter kept her black hat and large sunglasses on at all times backstage. Also ruling the runway were traditionally tall and thin models wearing ensembles that could barely be described as 'autumn or winter wear.' Cowan and his scantily-clad creations were just featured on the February 1 episode ('The Comeback') of America's Next Top Model on VH1. Meanwhile, it's unclear precisely when the former sex tape star will next man the decks at a DJ gig for a nightclub residency/event. And Cash Money Records has yet to put out Hilton's second album, which was supposed to include her singles - Crazy, Come Alive, and High Off My Love.
